msgid "If true, this actor will generate overlap Begin/End events when spawned as part of level streaming, which includes initial level load.\nYou might enable this is in the case where a streaming level loads around an actor and you want Begin/End overlap events to trigger.\n@see UpdateOverlapsMethodDuringLevelStreaming"
