#. Key:	Subsystem_WidgetModifier.K2Node_GetClassDefaults_1.ShowPinForProperties[17].PropertyTooltip
#. SourceLocation:	/KUI/ST_KUI.ST_KUI
#: /KUI/ST_KUI.ST_KUI
msgctxt "ST_KUI,Subsystem_WidgetModifier.K2Node_GetClassDefaults_1.ShowPinForProperties[17].PropertyTooltip"
msgid "If true, this actor will replicate to remote machines\n@see SetReplicates()"
