#. Key:	Subsystem_WidgetModifier.K2Node_GetClassDefaults_1.ShowPinForProperties[19].PropertyTooltip
#. SourceLocation:	/KUI/ST_KUI.ST_KUI
#: /KUI/ST_KUI.ST_KUI
msgctxt "ST_KUI,Subsystem_WidgetModifier.K2Node_GetClassDefaults_1.ShowPinForProperties[19].PropertyTooltip"
msgid "How long this Actor lives before dying, 0=forever. Note this is the INITIAL value and should not be modified once play has begun."
